title: VEG Deli
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Polish, Gluten-free
description: Modern, stylish two level restaurant serving vegan & gluten-free food and daily lunch special. Has a small take-out section selling spreads, jams, and baked goods all made in-house. Opened in Jan 2013. Reportedly no longer all vegan June 2014.
